                     JAMES NUTT (38), was indicted

                     for feloniously omitting to surrender himself to the Court of Bankruptcy, after having been adjudged a bankrupt; 



                     also, feloniously removing, concealing, and embezzling part of his personal estate, with intent to defraud his creditors; 



